{"title":"linux 虚拟机 ip配置","slug":"linux 项目部署/[Linux]  虚拟机 ip配置","date":"2021-01-18T15:08:49.876Z","updated":"2021-01-18T15:10:24.895Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux 项目部署/[Linux]  虚拟机 ip配置.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194042756.png","C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194127139.png","C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194310765.png","C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608196838177.png","C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608198200935.png"],"content":"<p>VMware创建linux虚拟机后，未设置网络不能上网</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>选用NAT模式</p>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194042756.png\" alt=\"1608194042756\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>主界面中点击 编辑&gt;虚拟网路编辑器</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置网段：192.168.178.0</li>\n<li>子网掩码：255.255.255.0</li>\n<li>设置子网IP： 192.168.178.0</li>\n<li>关闭DHCP</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194127139.png\" alt=\"1608194127139\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>配置 “NAT设置”</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置网关：192.168.178.254</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194310765.png\" alt=\"1608194310765\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>设置完，即可重启虚拟机进行安装</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在Centos7 设置IP</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>方法一： 自动分配IP</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置界面：Network&amp;Hostname点击 “ON”（开启DCHP才能自动分配ip）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>方法二：手动分配IP</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>ip addr show</p>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608196838177.png\" alt=\"1608196838177\" /></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-ens33</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608198200935.png\" alt=\"1608198200935\" /></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 修改以下</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">BOOTPROTO=static  <span class=\"comment\"># 修改为静态ip</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ONBOOT=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 添加</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">IPADDR=<span class=\"number\">192.168</span><span class=\"number\">.178</span><span class=\"number\">.110</span>  <span class=\"comment\"># 静态ip地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">NETMASK=<span class=\"number\">255.255</span><span class=\"number\">.255</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span>   <span class=\"comment\"># 子网掩码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">GATEWAY=<span class=\"number\">192.168</span><span class=\"number\">.178</span><span class=\"number\">.254</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 网关</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">DNS1=<span class=\"number\">119.29</span><span class=\"number\">.29</span><span class=\"number\">.29</span>       <span class=\"comment\"># 腾讯dns服务器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>重启网络服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl stop NetworkManager</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart network</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ssh远程连接\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ssh远程连接\"></a> SSH远程连接</h2>\n<p>SSH默认端口 22</p>\n","more":"<p>VMware创建linux虚拟机后，未设置网络不能上网</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>选用NAT模式</p>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194042756.png\" alt=\"1608194042756\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>主界面中点击 编辑&gt;虚拟网路编辑器</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置网段：192.168.178.0</li>\n<li>子网掩码：255.255.255.0</li>\n<li>设置子网IP： 192.168.178.0</li>\n<li>关闭DHCP</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194127139.png\" alt=\"1608194127139\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>配置 “NAT设置”</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置网关：192.168.178.254</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608194310765.png\" alt=\"1608194310765\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>设置完，即可重启虚拟机进行安装</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在Centos7 设置IP</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>方法一： 自动分配IP</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设置界面：Network&amp;Hostname点击 “ON”（开启DCHP才能自动分配ip）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>方法二：手动分配IP</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>ip addr show</p>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608196838177.png\" alt=\"1608196838177\" /></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-ens33</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5Cyango%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1608198200935.png\" alt=\"1608198200935\" /></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 修改以下</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">BOOTPROTO=static  <span class=\"comment\"># 修改为静态ip</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ONBOOT=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 添加</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">IPADDR=<span class=\"number\">192.168</span><span class=\"number\">.178</span><span class=\"number\">.110</span>  <span class=\"comment\"># 静态ip地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">NETMASK=<span class=\"number\">255.255</span><span class=\"number\">.255</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span>   <span class=\"comment\"># 子网掩码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">GATEWAY=<span class=\"number\">192.168</span><span class=\"number\">.178</span><span class=\"number\">.254</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 网关</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">DNS1=<span class=\"number\">119.29</span><span class=\"number\">.29</span><span class=\"number\">.29</span>       <span class=\"comment\"># 腾讯dns服务器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>重启网络服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl stop NetworkManager</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart network</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ssh远程连接\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ssh远程连接\"></a> SSH远程连接</h2>\n<p>SSH默认端口 22</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"linux","path":"api/categories/linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"linux","path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"虚拟机","path":"api/tags/虚拟机.json"}]}